data.title: World Soccer Autumn 2021
data.meta_description: World Soccer Autumn 2021_downmagaz.net - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides a preview of an upcoming special issue of the magazine "World Soccer" focusing on the 500 most important footballers in the world. It includes articles about Ronaldo's return to Manchester United, a reboot of La Masia youth academy, a new Japanese women's professional football league, and previews of the UEFA Nations League finals and various continental club competitions. The issue also features eyewitness reports from Afghanistan and Spain, an interview with coach Patrice Beaumelle, and a first-person account from Steve McManaman of his biggest game.
